body:
Hi, does tf-serving support SparseTensor? I'm afraid that SparseTensor is not a Tensor actually.

[ tf.saved_model.utils.build_tensor_info ](https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/tf/saved_model/utils/build_tensor_info)
> For SparseTensors, the names of the three constitutent Tensors are used.
